steps.html_instructions:
Head northwest on Karl-Liebknecht-Straße/B2/B5 toward Spandauer Str.
Continue to follow B2/B5
At Großer Stern, take the 3rd exit and stay on Str. des 17. Juni/B2/B5
At the roundabout, take the 3rd exit onto Bismarckstraße/B2/B5

Continue straight to stay on Bismarckstraße/B2/B5
Continue to follow B2/B5
Merge onto A100 via the ramp on the left to Dresden/Magdeburg/Leipzig/Flughafen Schönefeld/E51/Wilmersdorf
Keep left at the fork to continue on A9
At the interchange 33-Dreieck Bayerisches Vogtland, keep right and follow signs for A72 toward Plauen/Regensburg/Hof-Nord/A93/Tschechien
At the interchange 4-Dreieck Hochfranken, keep right and follow signs for A93 toward Regensburg/Prag/Praha/Tschechien/A6
At the interchange 55-Dreieck Holledau, keep left and follow signs for A9 toward München
Keep left at the fork to stay on A9, follow signs for München/Stuttgart/Lindau
Take exit 76-München-Schwabing on the left toward Mittlerer Ring Ost/Messe / ICM

Merge onto Schenkendorfstraße/B2R
Continue to follow B2R
